room_title: Escape room "Pirate Chest Quest" by Monroe Escape Rooms in Monroe (MI)
room_address: 14750 Laplaisance Road, Suite H30 Monroe, MI 48161
room_description: The Captain is missing and the crew of The Pirate Ship Odium wants their cut of his treasure and you have to help them get it! Find the clues, get the keys, unlock the locks, solve the puzzles and get into the mysteriously locked treasure chest before the ship sinks!
